{
 "name": "RPlog_Tonight_there_s_gonna_be_a_jailbreak",
 "title": "Tonight There's Gonna Be a Jailbreak: Thawing Malus at the Oubliette",
 "summary": "At the Oubliette, a secret Imperium supermax prison station where the galaxy's worst are entombed in carbonite, the Sith Mitra and the chaotic Twi'lek crime boss Skawn lead a stealth boarding party to extract a forgotten former emperor. Skawn's depraved crew floods the halls with slaughter while Mitra, accompanied by the wary mercenary Vix, cuts a precise path to the deep containment cell of the man called Malus. After fighting through droids, turrets, and guards--and sensing a dormant presence stirring beneath the ice--Skawn impatiently triggers the thawing process. Malus revives, cold and enraged, demanding to know how long he has been frozen and the whereabouts of Vassily, while Vix keeps her blaster trained on him and pushes the team to leave. Recognizing the danger of the station, Malus agrees to depart, and the extraction party withdraws to their ship with the resurrected emperor in tow.",
